cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.CR 

This paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning model for imbalanced classification, which involves sequential decision-making and deep Q-learning network. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and cryptography and security (cs.CR) as imbalanced classification is also relevant to security applications.
